The paper deals with the classification of music genres using lyrics, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and related topics. The paper also involves classification and machine learning, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of neural networks suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as a possible category. Finally, the paper involves data analysis and visualization, which could fall under cs.SD (Sound).
